{"tid":651964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★成日話金融業人工勁高，但滙豐 渣打股價明明衰過十年前","createTime":"2018-05-03T13:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T09:28:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"361863c76362abeb3d0c30b13cd032a2c595a142","tid":651964,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"why<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f85422429bae1013e54e8ede7f3261c6cbeab2a","tid":651964,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:25:54.000Z","msg":"呀!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"fc69cc81405abb913846fb53adcaa0a7d4ccd727","tid":651964,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:25:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">專家：金融及IT吃香</span><br />\n<br />\n2016/17年度年薪達90萬元以上的納稅人數目增至19.5萬，較去年18.2萬多，而年薪由60萬至90萬元的納稅人亦由20萬增至21.6萬，即年薪60萬元以上納稅人達41萬，佔整體23%。稅務局局長黃權輝被問繳交最高金額稅項人士的稅額，他指手頭上無資料。據悉，稅務局因私隱問題，近年已無公佈這批「打工皇帝」繳稅額。<br />\n高薪族大增，40萬元年薪或以下的納稅人數目則減少，跌幅最勁為20萬元或以下人士，由15/16年度40.2萬跌至16/17年度31.5萬，佔整體17.9%。<br />\n安俊人力資源顧問公司董事總經理周綺萍指，近年人力市場中以金融業較吃香，料不少高薪族來自該界別，「近1、2年較好景，唔少中資公司來港開新公司，挖角多，人工就有升」。資訊科技界亦十分缺人，因商界越來越着重互聯網發展，金融業亦鼓勵客人多用網上服務及網上保安，帶動業界加人工，估計兩界別一般工資有5至10%增長，若被挖角，人工更有兩至三成增幅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180503/20379815?_ga=2.30421631.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180503%2F20379815%3F_ga%3D2.30421631.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435&d=9taV22dOq6wRUAuP5TGQxTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=05c58ef7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180503%2F20379815%3F_ga%3D2.30421631.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435&h=93c89ac5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180503/20379815?_ga=2.30421631.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435</a>"},{"pid":"bdc9e1f272cc95078c1659f916080e7519e896bb","tid":651964,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:28:01.000Z","msg":"高薪養 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f902f4df11221a20b7b05db761b69fab80df29bd","tid":651964,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c027a81a64884fd0cdc3b1f4b0ed259d24291c","tid":651964,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:38:05.000Z","msg":"none know?"},{"pid":"1748722c9a8f6258683c7000c05d5376009ce970","tid":651964,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0331f074a857ea14d171bcbf9f40cd63c0dd3d","tid":651964,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:15:06.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"993a94d5825dab3cd7ae3102cefea363a0d36ad0","tid":651964,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0c027a81a64884fd0cdc3b1f4b0ed259d24291c","tid":651964,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:38:05.000Z","msg":"none know?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:20:03.000Z","msg":"X2"},{"pid":"85844afeee6a5646d6702d0af44b47be387884f7","tid":651964,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05